title: Bug 109350: Output parameter does not display in data set dialog
description: The output parameter should be displayed in the edit data set dialog while in the query result page.
OB: While in the query result page, there is no data returned. The actual result is that the output parameter does not display in the edit data set dialog.
EB: The output parameter should be displayed in the edit data set dialog while in the query result page.
SR:
To reproduce:
1. Open the query result page.
2. Verify that there is no data returned.
3. Check the edit data set dialog to see if the output parameter is displayed.
